name: Buton Girl and Umbrella
description:
This is portrait about Buton Girl who brings her umbrella.
Buton is one of Indonesia's tribe that has special character of eye colors. People in that tribe has two colors of eyes. One is blue and the other side is brown sometimes grey. This is so special although this is genetic disorder. 

The art coming from digital art, size 2000x2500 px 

The background is coming from my own photograph of leaf, just had inspired from nature.

Rainy day, sunny day or just colors find the way in this art, that is yours.
